    data=customer_behavior,
    x='segment'
)

plt.title('Customer Segmentation')
plt.xlabel('Customer Segment')
plt.ylabel('Number of Customers')

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()


Insight:
- Dominate by High Risk Customer that have a low completion rate or unstable transaction behavior.
- Regular customer have possibility to be upgrade as High Value customer.

Recommendation:
- Protect High Value Customers (Top Priority)
- Convert Regular → High Value (Quick Win)
- Contain High Risk Customers (Cost Control), action: Limitation for COD, Require prepayment untuk some categories, Fraud & cancellation threshold. The focus is not on full conversion, but on reducing losses and operational costs.

